OL,5, A care home resident was hit by a carer
OL,6, and had his food eaten by staff in the 
OL,7, days before his death, undercover      
OL,8, footage has revealed.                  
OL,10,FRon Carter, 82, died at The Gables in  
OL,11,FWhittlesey, Cambridgeshire, in May 2020
OL,12,Fabout six months after moving in.      
OL,14,FA hidden camera disguised as a clock in
OL,15,Fhis room recorded what the care        
OL,16,Fregulator has called "awful abuse".    
OL,18,FHC-One, which ran home, said the       
OL,19,Fbehaviour was "unacceptable" and has   
OL,20,Fapologised to the family.              
